  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u0026#34;Took in my late sister\u0026#39;s disabled cat, Rex. He was suffering... not anymore!\u0026#34;\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499287552/hB4426460/линеч\" id=\"_r_a_10499287552\" width=\"800\" height=\"1422\" alt=\"ЛИНЕЧ\" title=\"\u0026#34;Took in my late sister\u0026#39;s disabled cat, Rex. He was suffering... not anymore!\u0026#34;\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499287296/h196C5C5B/g-6984\" id=\"_r_a_10499287296\" width=\"800\" height=\"1422\" alt=\"G-6984\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is something that happens often. Cats are not often “mean”, not without reason. Our first instinct, when learning that a cat is mean to humans, is trying to figure out if the cat is being treated well, and more often than not, the cat is not. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499285248/h78DA3505/he-always-so-mean-everyone-but-my-sister-and-her-husband-he-born-with-his-arms-bent-hes-squitten\" id=\"_r_a_10499285248\" width=\"774\" height=\"353\" alt=\"He\u0026#39;s always been known as \u0026#34;demon cat\u0026#34; because he was always so mean to everyone but my sister and her husband. He was born with his arms bent in. He\u0026#39;s a Squitten.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499284736/h91B95077/as-my-sister-raised-him-by-hand-as-my-cat-had-him-as-kitten-and-rejected-him-kept-his-brother\" id=\"_r_a_10499284736\" width=\"704\" height=\"371\" alt=\"He lives like a normal cat. He kind of acts more like a dog than a cat. He always had temperament issues as my sister raised him by hand as my cat had him as a kitten and rejected him. I kept his brother.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499285760/hA62407B6/and-learned-she-living-way-worse-than-she-let-us-onto-hoarder-level-with-5-dogs-2-cats-and-birds\" id=\"_r_a_10499285760\" width=\"720\" height=\"374\" alt=\"My sister passed on Christmas eve of 2024. Its been a few months. The night it happened we went to her house and learned she was living way worse than she let us onto. Hoarder level with 5 dogs, 2 cats, and birds.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499285504/h953B8FEE/been-doing-great-with-grief-and-went-get-help-my-family-took-all-pets-rex-became-my-responsibility\" id=\"_r_a_10499285504\" width=\"720\" height=\"423\" alt=\"We cleaned the house as much as we could, 12 family member effort. My brother in law hasn\u0026#39;t been doing great with grief and went to get help. My family took in all the pets, Rex became my responsibility.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499284992/h6BD167A6/he-so-matted-got-him-covered-dried-pee-and-whatever-else-dust-could-get-trapped-under-his-fur\" id=\"_r_a_10499284992\" width=\"722\" height=\"367\" alt=\"Him living in a hoarder house did a lot to him physically and mentally. He was so matted when I got him, covered in dried pee, , and whatever else dust could get trapped under his fur.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499286016/hA63127AC/shave-up-until-halfway-point-on-his-tail-as-shaved-him-he-happily-flead-and-groomed-his-front-legs\" id=\"_r_a_10499286016\" width=\"696\" height=\"602\" alt=\"Overweight because he couldn\u0026#39;t move around anywhere. His nails were so overgrown since he can\u0026#39;t claw a post like normal. I got him shaved, all the mats off. I had to shave up until the halfway point on his tail. As I shaved him, he happily flead and groomed his front legs.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499286528/h6AE9FE08/but-got-him-free-mats-next-clipped-his-nails-he-gave-no-fights-and-enjoyed-pets-my-partner-as-did\" id=\"_r_a_10499286528\" width=\"725\" height=\"364\" alt=\"He didn\u0026#39;t fight it until he got tired and wanted to be alone. It took me a few sessions but I got him free of the mats. Next i clipped his nails, he gave no fights, and enjoyed pets from my partner as I did it.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499286272/hE17A431B/fighting-he-did-such-good-job-and-only-got-mad-tried-dry-him-understandable-my-toddler-does-same\" id=\"_r_a_10499286272\" width=\"706\" height=\"310\" alt=\"My other sister helped give him a bath. Zero fighting. He did such a good job and only got mad when I tried to dry him. Understandable. My toddler does the same.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499286784/hAC0FD11F/grab-our-hands-bring-them-back-his-face-if-pull-away-he-purrs-so-loud-never-heard-him-purr-before\" id=\"_r_a_10499286784\" width=\"724\" height=\"312\" alt=\"He\u0026#39;s so happy to see us and get pets now. He reaches up and tries to grab our hands to bring them back to his face if we pull away. He purrs so loud. I never heard him purr before.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499287040/hAE1DA516/12-will-be-spent-happy-and-clean-bonus-angry-boy-day-he-came-home-pic-and-baby-rex-picture-at-end\" id=\"_r_a_10499287040\" width=\"731\" height=\"539\" alt=\"I wish i could have helped him and my sister before all of this. But I\u0026#39;m sure my sister is happy that Rex\u0026#39;s last few years (he\u0026#39;s 12) will be spent happy and clean. Bonus angry boy the day he came home pic, and baby Rex picture at the end!!\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10499287808/hF1B5DA66\" id=\"_r_a_10499287808\" width=\"800\" height=\"1421\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10499287808\" title=\"\" 